<h3 class="card-title">Company Story</h3>
<p>
    With the aim of creating Singapore's most extensive and immersive consumer lifestyle marketplaces,
    Chris and Jet's management of the CJ Tech Show brings together top brands and innovators for a dynamic and diverse product showcase held quarterly. 
    Each event is carefully curated, providing consumers with the opportunity to explore the latest trends and products in consumer technology while enjoying exceptional deals. 
    The series includes flagship events like COMEX and ITSHOW, along with The Tech Show and Consumer Electronics Exhibition (CEE).
</p>
